</li> </ul>
</li>
<li class="gem-c-document-list__item">
<a class="gem-c-document-list__item-title gem-c-document-list__item-link" data-ecommerce-index="3" data-ecommerce-path="/maib-reports/safety-warning-about-the-securing-of-retractable-keels-or-retractable-weighted-centreboards" data-ecommerce-row="1" data-track-action="Marine Accident Investigation Branch reports.3" data-track-category="navFinderLinkClicked" data-track-label="/maib-reports/safety-warning-about-the-securing-of-retractable-keels-or-retractable-weighted-centreboards" data-track-options='{"dimension28":50,"dimension29":"Safety warning about the securing of retractable keels or retractable weighted centreboards"}' href="/maib-reports/safety-warning-about-the-securing-of-retractable-keels-or-retractable-weighted-centreboards">Safety warning about the securing of retractable keels or retractable weighted centreboards</a>
<p class="gem-c-document-list__item-description">Urgent safety lesson issued after a fatal inversion of a sailing boat with a retractable keel.</p>
